author: Soo Kim
title: Only 1 Percent of U.S. Population Has Been Tested for Coronavirus
description: Less than one percent have been tested for the virus in both Texas and California.
content: The novel coronavirus in the U.S. has infected at least 825,600 people, as of Wednesday. But with less than two percent of Americans tested for the virus so far, according to the latest figures from Johns Hopkins University, the infected population is likely … [+7553 chars]
